<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>الاَقتصاد والرفق فِي المعيشة <span class="c2">(٥٤٣١ ــ ٥٤٦٧)</span> جـ <span class="c2">(٣)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>الاَقتصاد فِي الأعمال ــ بِالتَّعَصُّبْ <span class="c2">(٨٤١١ ــ ٨٤٢٥)</span> جـ <span class="c2">(٣)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">بِالتَّعَصُّب:</span> أََوْغِلْ فِيهِ بِرِفق <span class="c2">(٥٢٩٢ ــ ٥٤٣٠)</span> جـ <span class="c2">(٣)</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>المعاملة مع أهل الذمة <span class="c2">(٤١٦٣٢ ــ ٤١٦٧٧)</span> جـ <span class="c2">(١٥)</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
